Magnues looks at the femm bot. His eyes narrow on the decepticon ensignia. "I 
have seen many thing, but i never dreamt id see a decepticon walking around  
a base of my friends....such things can be expected in these turbelent time. 
Your a telepath arent you...I can tell I can see the wavelengthes emenating 
from you. Prime taught me to block and recognize people with such 
abilites...." Suddenly  Magnus grabbed his chest his breath short and 
stuttered. One knee dropped to the ground leaving a small dent. The pain 
faded and he stood back up. His breath still shallow. "Im getting old friend 
I dont nkow how much more of this stuff my spark can take."

--part1_149.7b73ff.2adde3e0_boundary
